                "text": "<p>B2B digital commerce is increasingly competitive, and staying ahead of competitors requires a digital commerce foundation built for B2B. Many platforms built for B2C look appropriate for B2B at first glance- but in reality they cannot handle the complexities of B2B commerce. As more manufactures and distributors join the online commerce world, rigid legacy platforms cannot keep the pace needed to win business in the current environment.</p>\n"
