        },
        "content": "<p>Virto Commerce provides industry leading order management functionality. It can be integrated into complex enterprise workflows -- including many leading ERP and fulfillment systems.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Customer order history</li>\n\t<li>Split shipments</li>\n\t<li>Split payments</li>\n\t<li>Punchout support</li>\n\t<li>Quotes and purchase orders</li>\n\t<li>Subscription management</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "url1": null,
