        "content": "<p>Virto Commerce&#39;s modular architecture supports REST based APIs. These APIs allow you integrate other business systems and frontend technologies, such as customer profile data or a chat bot, into your Virto Commerce solution.Virto Commerce can support all your B2B pricing needs. Prices can be personalized in real-time based on audience, campaign, purchase history, geo-location, contracts and other customer-based scenarios.</p>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Modular architecture to customize your solution</li>\n\t<li>Real-time exchange of data&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Secure: REST Oauth and token based authentication ensures your data will never be breeched&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://admin-demo.virtocommerce.com/docs/ui/index\">Explore our API</a></p>\n",
